  <brief_title>The Effects of Epidural Anesthesia on the Bioavailability of Nitric Oxide and Renal Function in Patients Undergoing Laparoscopic Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effects of Epidural Anesthesia on the Bioavailability of Nitric Oxide and Renal Function in Patients Undergoing Laparoscopic Surgery</official_title>
